snippet.title: "Happy Hotel" Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Happy Hotel, where the halls are filled with mystery, eerie encounters, and relentless anomalies waiting to surprise you at every turn. Step into this mildly horror-themed experience and test your nerves as you navigate through shadowy hallways, dodge deadly traps, and face off with “Happy”—the unsettling bunny who won’t let you go easily.

Do you have what it takes to survive the night? Wishlist Happy’s Hotel on Steam and be the first to check in when it releases on 11/26!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/3295230/Happy_Hotel/
